.TH erealms legacy_adapter "2019-01-19"
.SH NAME
Elemental Realms Legacy Adapter \- used to convert mysql data into json
.SH SYNOPSIS
er_legacy_adapter 
.B mysql://USERNAME:PASSWORD@IP/DATABASE_NAME
.I [OPTIONS]
.SH OPTIONS
.IP "Em [file path]"
exports a list of all mods
.IP "Ev [file path]"
exports versions
.IP PS
a simplistic debug parameter that gives a indication of what the program is doing
.IP "mode [00-01-10-11]"
 sets what versions should be included in export
 10 (Visable: true Dev- false) is the default.
 e.g.
 if you also wanted dev versions: 
.B mode 10-11
